		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know there are a ton a tools that can create bitmap pictures on the GBA for bitmap modes, (obviously) but does anyone know of a program comparable to pcx2snes except for the GBA that would help make tile based graphics? It would also be nice if it had a screen mode like pcx2snes, as you wouldn't even have to make a tilemap yourself because the GBA does not have tile priority on BGs.

		

